&lt;/div&gt;

  
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://cva4.com/images/2026/nvidia-smi.png&#34; alt=&#34;PyTorch&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Video tutorial&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;video-tutorial&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#video-tutorial&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

    
